# =============================================================================
# Root .gitignore — Catch-all safety net
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# `backend/.gitignore` y `frontend/.gitignore` cubren el grueso de su
# sub-árbol. Este archivo agrega:
#   • Patrones cross-subdir por si una herramienta genera artefactos donde
#     no había gitignore propio (e.g., un `node_modules/` que aparezca a
#     raíz durante un `pnpm install` mal apuntado).
#   • IDEs / editors con state global.
#   • Working memory del agente: SOLO el delta de la última sesión NO
#     entra al repo (agent-summary.md); el CURRENT.md acumulado SÍ.
# =============================================================================

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# --- Backup / swap / temp / merge conflict leftovers ---
*.swp
*.swo
*.bak
*.tmp
*~
.~lock.*
*.orig
*.rej

# --- Node / pnpm / npm defensivo (coverage cross-subdir) ---
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp.*
**/.pnp.js

# --- Build artifacts (cualquier subdir sin gitignore propio) ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.next/
**/.nuxt/
**/out/

# --- Coverage / test artifacts ---
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/
**/*.lcov

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# --- TypeScript incremental build cache ---
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Environments (.env → NO committed, .env.example → SÍ) ---
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.development.local
.env.test
.env.test.local
.env.production
.env.production.local
!**/.env.example
!**/*.env.example

# --- Editors / IDEs ---
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
*.iml

# --- Working memory del agente (per-session) ---
# `agent-memory/CURRENT.md` ES project memory → tracked.
# `agent-summary.md` (root) es el delta de la ÚLTIMA sesión → NO tracked.
agent-summary.md
agent-summary.*.md

# --- Docker / compose noise ---
**/.docker/
**/docker-compose.override.yml
**/docker-compose.*.yml
!docker-compose.yml

# --- Misc build caches ---
**/.cache/
**/.parcel-cache/
**/.rollup.cache/
**/.turbo/
**/.tsserver/
